Moreover, the growing trend towards plant-based diets and lifestyles is further fueling the demand for non-dairy alternatives in the beverage market. Plant-based milk options such as oat milk, almond milk, and cashew milk are gaining popularity among consumers seeking dairy-free and sustainable choices. This trend aligns with the broader movement towards sustainable and environmentally friendly practices in the food and beverage industry, driving the adoption of plant-based ingredients in beverage formulations.

